        <num>CC 2048</num>
        <heading>2048.  Words susceptible of different meanings</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2048.  Words susceptible of different meanings
Words susceptible of different meanings must be interpreted as having the meaning that best conforms to the object of the contract.</p>
        </content>
